I saw this on the GECCO web page and thought it was interesting.

I note GECCO as 7th. ECAL also made the list. AAAI was number one (congrats
to Jason and Ken for getting in there!).

Notable absences are alife, CEC, PPSN, and IEEE alife, amongst others.

http://www.cs-conference-ranking.org/conferencerankings/topicsii.html
